item.title: EcoStar Launches Its New 4K Android 11 LED TV Series
item.description: EcoStar has launched a new Android 11 LED TV with the latest operating system and software version. In terms of picture quality, you can choose from HD, FHD, or UHD 4K on an Android LED TV.
